Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.88,0:00:08.66,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,A spotless uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.44,0:00:11.20,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,A brand-new bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.20,0:00:12.65,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,A pristine notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.58,0:00:16.41,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,My entrance ceremony is tomorrow at last!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.08,0:00:20.28,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,The start of my high school career!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.08,0:00:28.04,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,My tummy hurts just thinking about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.00,0:00:28.04,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(359,1)\bord1\fnComic Sans MS\c&HBF4242&\3c&HF5F3F2&\pos(106.666,158)}Stab stab stab
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.37,0:00:33.05,Narration,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Life on Earth is full of challenges for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.60,0:00:37.40,Narration,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I just know that I won't be able to \Ntalk to anyone, or make any friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.40,0:00:39.06,Narration,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,as time passes me by...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.07,0:00:41.02,Narration,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,After all...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.40,0:00:47.58,Narration,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,What I say won't reach anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.67,0:00:51.57,Narration,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Not a single person on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.99,0:00:54.89,Narration,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,But out there somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.89,0:00:57.91,Narration,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Surely there must be someone it can reach...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.91,0:00:59.05,Default,Popipupians,0000,0000,0000,,Umika!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.45,0:01:02.04,Default,Popipupians,0000,0000,0000,,It reached us just fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.91,0:01:06.51,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, aliens!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.16,0:01:11.42,Narration,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,If I could just go somewhere else,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.61,0:01:14.67,Narration,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I know that I could find someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.63,0:01:18.93,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,A shooting star! No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.81,0:01:23.18,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could meet an alien!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.92,0:01:30.53,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Did I make it in time?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.79,0:01:38.30,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Starting tomorrow, maybe I'll \Ntry just a little harder...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.90,0:01:50.82,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,That was a good nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.86,0:01:53.10,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.10,0:01:53.96,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
