Dialogue: 1,0:03:35.06,0:03:35.73,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, all!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.97,0:03:37.91,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to your new school!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.91,0:03:40.61,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Akane Emihara, and I'll be \Nyour homeroom teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.85,0:03:46.07,DefaultTop,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,My name's written with the character for \N"smile," so I hope you can smile here, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.20,0:03:46.42,Narration,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Umika Konohoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.07,0:03:49.76,DefaultTop,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Let's kick things off and have \Neveryone introduce themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.42,0:03:49.25,Narration,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fifteen years old, and as of today, \NI'm in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.76,0:03:53.14,Narration,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Like everyone else, I'm a normal Earthling...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.62,0:03:55.25,Narration,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.62,0:03:55.75,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.2\fs28\fnComic Sans MS\c&H544F83&\fax-0.2\frz7.135\pos(294,47.334)\b0}Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.46,0:03:57.88,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,My drawing came out well!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.88,0:03:59.63,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(483,1)\fnComic Sans MS\fs14\pos(327.333,10)}Homeroom teacher:\NAkane Emihara\N\NSelf-introductions\Nv\NEntrance ceremony
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.88,0:03:59.63,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,You over there! Pay attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.90,0:04:03.77,Narration,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,And I get yelled at a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.14,0:04:07.68,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I've embarrassed myself already...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.68,0:04:08.63,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.45,0:04:12.00,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Introductions are always so nerve-wracking.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.00,0:04:13.52,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Relax, relax!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.73,0:04:15.00,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.79,0:04:21.28,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Not again...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.28,0:04:22.89,DefaultTop,Kinashi,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone calls me Nasshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.32,0:04:26.45,Narration,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not good at talking to people.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.89,0:04:25.73,DefaultTop,Kinashi,0000,0000,0000,,I want to continue playing \Nvolleyball in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.73,0:04:27.41,DefaultTop,Kinashi,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.41,0:04:29.16,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.2\fnComic Sans MS\c&HF1F5ED&\fay-0.25\pos(542.667,80.667)}Self-introductions
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.41,0:04:29.16,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, same here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.55,0:04:30.70,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,You're up next, Konohoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.74,0:04:33.41,Narration,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,The words just won't come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.41,0:04:34.04,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.04,0:04:35.42,Narration,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,They get stuck in my throat,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.42,0:04:37.04,Narration,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,and my face turns red.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.04,0:04:40.17,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I-I-I'm... Umika Konohoshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.56,0:04:44.43,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I h-hope we can all get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.43,0:04:46.05,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.53,0:04:47.54,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Sasaki, you're next!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.80,0:04:47.14,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(278,1)\fs40\fnComic Sans MS\c&H292E25&\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord1.5\pos(95.334,256.666)}Sigh
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.14,0:04:47.34,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\fnComic Sans MS\c&H292E25&\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord1.5\pos(95.334,256.666)}Siigh
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.34,0:04:47.55,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\fnComic Sans MS\c&H292E25&\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord1.5\pos(95.334,256.666)}Siiigh
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.54,0:04:48.30,Default,Sasaki,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.55,0:04:47.72,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\fnComic Sans MS\c&H292E25&\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord1.5\pos(95.334,256.666)}Siiiigh
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.72,0:04:48.30,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,263)\fs40\fnComic Sans MS\c&H292E25&\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord1.5\pos(95.334,256.666)}Siiiiigh
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.91,0:04:51.39,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I really am hopeless!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.01,0:04:56.43,Narration,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I can't talk or laugh normally \Nlike everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.43,0:04:58.02,Narration,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,It's like I'm from another planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.02,0:04:58.64,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,All righty!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.02,0:05:03.40,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.2\an7\fs20\fnComic Sans MS\pos(444.667,28.667)}Homeroom teacher:\NAkane Emihara
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.02,0:05:03.40,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.2\an7\fs20\fnComic Sans MS\pos(342.667,28.667)}Self-\Nintroductions
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.02,0:05:03.40,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.2\an7\fs20\fnComic Sans MS\pos(241.334,28.667)}Entrance\Nceremony
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.64,0:05:00.73,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone line up in the hallway!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.73,0:05:02.92,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Next stop: the entrance ceremony!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.92,0:05:06.91,Narration,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,There's nowhere left for me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.24,0:05:11.16,Narration,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,But I know that out there somewhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.16,0:05:16.26,Narration,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,there are glorious worlds where my \Nwords and feelings can reach others:
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.48,0:05:22.11,Narration,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,the radiant, far-off worlds \Nthat I read stories of as a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.67,0:05:25.05,Narration,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I won't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.05,0:05:28.43,Narration,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go and find somewhere \NI belong, all by myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.80,0:05:29.93,Narration,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,If Earth isn't for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.32,0:05:31.43,Narration,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.82,0:05:33.43,Narration,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go to outer space!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.43,0:05:36.01,Narration,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,If no one on this planet can understand me,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.01,0:05:41.02,Narration,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I just need to find a planet \Nwith people who do!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.28,0:05:43.05,Narration,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,According to my research,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.05,0:05:47.78,Narration,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,some aliens out there can \Ncommunicate telepathically!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.53,0:05:47.78,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(483,1)\fs28\fnArial Black\c&H5DF3FD&\3c&H492930&\4c&H492930&\bord1.5\shad2\fay-0.5\frx-15\pos(310,88.666)}So awesome!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.10,0:05:51.28,Narration,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I'll find aliens who can understand me,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.28,0:05:53.04,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\t(30,1740,\fscy107.96)\t(30,1740,\fscx107.96)\fs16\bord2\frx20\fnTimes New Roman\c&H16180C&\3c&HFCFDFB&\move(320,174,319.89,173.4,30,1740)}Fujinomisaki Prefectural High School Entrance Ceremony
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.28,0:05:56.29,Narration,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,and I'll prove that there's \Na place where I fit in!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.54,0:05:57.79,Narration,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,You can do it, Umika!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.79,0:05:59.04,Narration,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Keep fighting, Umika!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.04,0:06:02.04,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I'm late!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.04,0:06:03.80,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Class 1-A, third on the roster!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.80,0:06:07.17,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,My spaceship broke down, so I got here late!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.17,0:06:08.77,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,What? Spaceship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.77,0:06:09.68,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.68,0:06:13.06,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Um, my student ID should be here...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.06,0:06:16.06,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,The name's Yu Akeuchi, and I'm an alien!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.06,0:06:17.81,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Hope we get along!
