Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.81,0:06:20.31,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.54,0:06:23.69,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.24,0:06:27.95,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't expecting a close encounter \Nof the third kind so soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.95,0:06:30.21,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Spaceships? Aliens?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.21,0:06:31.41,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.41,0:06:32.76,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I need to talk to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.46,0:06:36.85,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.85,0:06:38.46,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I got...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.46,0:06:40.78,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,this alien language dictionary!
