Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.72,0:06:47.09,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Pe... pe... pegi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.09,0:06:49.72,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Sho hard! Alien language is hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.72,0:06:50.63,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.63,0:06:52.85,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Be brave, Umika!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.09,0:06:52.85,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnGeorgia\c&H5DC0CB&\3c&H300A81&\bord2\pos(320,14)}Alien Language\NDictionary\N{\fs12}Second Edition
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.85,0:06:55.64,Default,Kaneda,0000,0000,0000,,That thing you did at the \Nentrance ceremony was wild!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.64,0:06:56.51,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,That thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.51,0:06:58.56,Default,Kaneda,0000,0000,0000,,When you went, "I'm an alien!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.56,0:07:01.77,Default,Kinashi,0000,0000,0000,,What an eye-opening way \Nto make your big entrance!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.77,0:07:04.42,Default,Kaneda,0000,0000,0000,,That alien stuff really freaked me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.90,0:07:07.03,Default,Kinashi,0000,0000,0000,,You should have picked a better joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.26,0:07:08.22,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Joke...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.71,0:07:10.90,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I should have realized it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.90,0:07:14.57,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I'd come \Nacross an alien so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.07,0:07:17.47,Flashback,Girl A,0000,0000,0000,,Aliens don't really exist!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.47,0:07:19.53,Flashback,Girl B,0000,0000,0000,,You're such a baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.53,0:07:20.69,Flashback,Girl C,0000,0000,0000,,UFOs?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.69,0:07:22.66,Flashback,Girl C,0000,0000,0000,,That's just make-believe on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.66,0:07:25.90,Flashback,Girl D,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious about finding aliens?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.90,0:07:28.00,Flashback,Girl E,0000,0000,0000,,I saw it on TV the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.00,0:07:30.67,Flashback,Girl E,0000,0000,0000,,They said that humanity \Nwon't ever encounter aliens.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.67,0:07:32.68,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs15\c&HC3C3C3&\3c&H10110E&\bord3}The chances of humanity encountering intelligent extraterrestrial lifeforms...\NAs for places within our solar system where the possibility of life exists...\NAlthough moons like Europa are often suggested, intelligent...\NThe possibility that they exist is close to zero. In the vast...\NSearching for a planet with intelligent life on it...\NWe can infer that the natural continuation of human civilization...\NThis supports the opinion that such a discovery is impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.11,0:07:32.27,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.30,0:07:36.56,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.56,0:07:37.81,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.05,0:07:39.31,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.31,0:07:47.07,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur0.2\fs36\frx-15\fnGeorgia\c&H5CC4CD&\move(312,102.445,312,122.445,108,525)}Alien Language\NDictionary
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.50,0:07:43.86,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,My people, the ones my words can reach...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.86,0:07:46.37,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I'll definitely find them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.37,0:07:47.07,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.31,0:07:49.07,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I know that book!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.25,0:07:54.49,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Um... hello, hello...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.49,0:07:56.30,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Pe... pe...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.30,0:07:57.08,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.32,0:08:00.16,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Peggyov movrovbivuubavuv vuv!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.95,0:08:02.04,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.04,0:08:05.52,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Pronouncing the voiced consonants \Nis the hard part of alien language!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.52,0:08:08.99,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Imagine green magma bubbling up \Nfrom deep within the earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.99,0:08:10.92,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,and say it real loud, \Nright from the diaphragm!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.92,0:08:12.56,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Movrov! Movrov!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.56,0:08:14.49,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Mo... mo... mo...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.49,0:08:16.50,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.50,0:08:18.06,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Movrov! Movrov!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.06,0:08:19.93,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Mo, mo, mo...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.93,0:08:22.64,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you're red as a beet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.64,0:08:24.38,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a cold? Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.38,0:08:26.94,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,No, this isn't a cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.94,0:08:28.87,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Um, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.37,0:08:30.94,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Lemme see your forehead real quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.16,0:08:41.79,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Stress, worries, shock, anxiety...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.18,0:08:45.72,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,A great longing... for outer space?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.50,0:08:51.30,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't seem like a fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.30,0:08:52.59,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,That's a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.15,0:08:54.81,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.35,0:09:00.05,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,When we touched, it was like all \Nof my feelings were laid bare...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.47,0:09:02.06,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost like...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.60,0:09:07.15,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for scaring you, \NEarthling Umika Konohoshi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.85,0:09:10.23,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,That was foreheadpathy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.17,0:09:15.74,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,It's my—Yu Akeuchi's—special alien power!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.09,0:09:18.62,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Forehead...pathy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.62,0:09:23.25,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like no one else believes I'm an alien.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.83,0:09:25.87,Narration,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Akeuchi-san, sulking as she said that,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.87,0:09:29.44,Narration,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,seemed so innocent, mysterious, \Nand yet somehow warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.14,0:09:34.61,Narration,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I felt something from her, \Ndifferent from the Earthlings I knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.54,0:09:40.01,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,A real... alien?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.29,0:09:40.98,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:40.98,0:09:44.64,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna be friends! I wanna be \Nfriends! I wanna be friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.31,0:09:44.64,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(813,1)\bord3\fnComic Sans MS\an9\fs26\pos(630,14.667)\c&HE5E5E5&\3c&H2C362E&}I wanna be friends I wanna be\Nwanna be friends I wanna be friends\NI wanna be friends I wanna be\Nwanna be friends I wanna be friends\NI wanna be friends I wanna be\Nwanna be friends I wanna be friends\NI wanna be friends I wanna be\Nwanna be friends I wanna be friends\NI wanna be friends I wanna be\Nwanna be friends I wanna be friends
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.64,0:09:46.75,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,An alien! An alien! An alien!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.64,0:09:47.14,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,513)\an4\q2\bord3\fnComic Sans MS\an9\fs26\c&HE5E5E5&\3c&H2C362E&\move(5,30,-800,30,27,2488)}An alien   Friends with an alien   Alien!   Be my friend   Friends with an alien   An alien, an alien   Be my friend   Friends   Friends   Alien   Friends with an alien   An alien   Friends, friends   Alien!   Be my friend, friends   Alien   Friends, alien   Be my friend   Alien   Friends   Be my
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.75,0:09:48.92,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Be my friend! Be my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.97,0:09:50.03,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Umika? Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.92,0:09:50.40,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,An alien! Friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.40,0:09:51.56,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.56,0:09:52.65,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Umika?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.65,0:09:55.65,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\t(26,2987,\fscy111.87)\t(26,2987,\fscx111.87)\blur0.2\b0\fs24\fnComic Sans MS\c&H616488&\frz53.18\move(220.44,114.89,186.73,110.21,26,2987)}Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.35,0:09:55.65,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Umika!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.44,0:09:55.65,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(654,1)\t(28,2197,\fscy108.72)\t(28,2197,\fscx108.72)\b0\fs24\fnComic Sans MS\c&H616488&\fax0.1\frz4.656\move(421.11,32.89,413.87,22.4,28,2197)}Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.27,0:09:59.16,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Where? Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.16,0:10:00.66,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,My friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.20,0:10:04.67,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I want to meet an alien...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.67,0:10:05.79,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.79,0:10:08.48,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Yu Akeuchi, an alien!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.48,0:10:09.54,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meetcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.24,0:10:14.44,Narration,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,That encounter today took me \Nby so much surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.09,0:10:17.90,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wow! Oh, wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.90,0:10:20.84,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I might have finally met an alien!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.10,0:10:24.72,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,If Akeuchi-san turns out \Nto be a real alien,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.60,0:10:29.48,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,would she let me be her friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.34,0:10:31.86,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.98,0:10:35.76,Narration,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,My words that can't reach anyone here...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.76,0:10:37.64,Narration,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Will she be the one to accept them?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.37,0:10:45.62,Signs_Boxed,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&H33&\an7\bord0\blur0.2\p1\c&HF0F3F2&\pos(384,12)\fscx245\fscy152}m 0 0 l 100 0 100 100 0 100
Dialogue: 1,0:10:41.37,0:10:45.62,Signs_Boxed,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnComic Sans MS\an7\fs12\c&H363637&\3c&H363637&\pos(395,18)}\h\h\h{\u1}Introducing myself{\u0}\N1. Greeting: Hello.\N2. Name: My name is Umika Konohoshi.\N3. Home planet: I'm an Earthling, born on Earth.\N4. Size: My height is 151 cm.\N\h\h\h{\s1}My weight is {\bord1}\h\h\h\h\h{\bord0\s0} No!!\N5. Hobbies: Reading novels. I really like sci-fi\N\h\h\hand mystery stories.\N6. Skills: I'm a little good at swimming.\N7. Lifelong dream: I want to build a rocket to go to\N\h\h\houter space and find aliens who will be my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.79,0:10:45.62,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,If I want to be her friend, I need \Nto properly introduce myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.62,0:10:49.12,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I need to tell Akeuchi-san all about myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.36,0:10:53.50,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I stayed up all night rehearsing \Nit in my head, so I'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.38,0:10:57.35,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Also, I get nervous when \Nother people are around,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.35,0:11:00.23,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,so I need to find a way to \Nbe alone with Akeuchi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.23,0:11:01.28,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.83,0:11:02.34,Default,Group,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.28,0:11:02.34,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Mornin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.34,0:11:03.14,Default,Group,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.53,0:11:07.89,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's the hardest part.
