Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.16,0:11:11.02,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Class orientation!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.02,0:11:12.93,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,It's time for an Emihara class tradition!
