Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.93,0:11:16.02,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,The tag-team scavenger hunt game is on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.02,0:11:17.26,Default,Group,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.26,0:11:18.67,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,The rules are simple!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.67,0:11:22.46,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Each team of two must find task cards \Nscattered across campus
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.46,0:11:25.13,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,and complete the tasks written on them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.99,0:11:25.78,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(528,1)\fs40\fnArial Black\c&HADA59F&\4c&HADA59F&\3c&H43413F&\bord1.5\shad2\pos(422,66.667)}Loner
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.54,0:11:28.79,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I need to work up the courage \Nand ask Akeuchi-san to...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.08,0:11:31.86,Default,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Also, all teams will be decided by lottery!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.46,0:11:32.54,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(528,1)\fs30\fnArial Black\c&HADA59F&\4c&HADA59F&\3c&H43413F&\bord1.5\shad2\pos(386.666,140)}Luck
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.54,0:11:33.67,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial Black\c&HDFDFE4&\bord2\fax0.1\3c&H4836DC&\pos(299.333,294)}LOTTERY
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.84,0:11:35.92,DefaultTop,Uno,0000,0000,0000,,Five!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.84,0:11:38.06,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,No, if I draw the same number as Akeuchi-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.92,0:11:38.06,DefaultTop,Uno,0000,0000,0000,,Who drew a five?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.06,0:11:40.27,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have my chance to talk with her!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.27,0:11:41.68,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I can't give in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.68,0:11:42.09,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,389)\fs40\fnArial Black\c&HE8DFE3&\bord2\frx20\fsp3\3c&H423CDC&\frz1.116\pos(335.555,260.445)}LOTTERY
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.15,0:11:44.64,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I need to believe in my own luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.64,0:11:48.30,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I drew two of the same number!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.81,0:11:51.90,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go, Umika!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.90,0:11:53.10,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Let's pair up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.64,0:11:56.06,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,U-Umika?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.38,0:11:57.32,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Go, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.32,0:11:59.57,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Let's work hard to finish this thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.80,0:12:03.41,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I can't waste the chance Akeuchi-san gave me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.95,0:12:07.83,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I need to tell her about myself, \Nin my own words!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.12,0:12:11.33,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're real fired up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.59,0:12:12.48,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.48,0:12:14.33,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'm excited, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.27,0:12:16.59,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Is it here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.28,0:12:18.34,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.00,0:12:20.34,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,It's gotta be here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.56,0:12:21.42,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.42,0:12:22.17,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Or here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.17,0:12:23.34,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Here, maybe?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.34,0:12:25.43,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,She really made them hard to find!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.56,0:12:28.19,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can't find the right time...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.19,0:12:29.39,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.39,0:12:31.27,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Umika, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.14,0:12:34.48,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.25,0:12:37.48,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even talk to Earthlings,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.48,0:12:41.23,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,so why did I think I could talk to an alien?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.36,0:12:49.12,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(109,1)\fs40\fnArial Black\c&H9F8B88&\4c&H422B2A&\3c&HB9B2AB&\bord1\shad2\move(336,87.334,424.667,90.001,3362,3904)\t(3362,3904,\fscx85\fscy85}Communication
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.47,0:12:45.21,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I had to know it would be just \Nas difficult to communicate!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.21,0:12:46.45,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.45,0:12:49.12,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure we'll find a card in no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.12,0:12:50.11,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Umika?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.11,0:12:52.21,DefaultTop,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Everything will be a-okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.11,0:12:53.37,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Is there even any point \Nin introducing myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.86,0:12:57.38,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,What if she laughs at me for \Nbeing childish, like the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.38,0:12:59.48,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Akeuchi-san says she's an alien,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.48,0:13:03.13,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,but even that might end up being a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.13,0:13:04.26,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Umika!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.66,0:13:06.13,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Look me in the eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.01,0:13:16.11,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Umika, you're really nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.11,0:13:18.40,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,And you feel really lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.84,0:13:22.08,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm right here, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.08,0:13:23.40,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,You're so silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.38,0:13:28.92,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Umika, isn't there something \Nyou want to tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.44,0:13:31.50,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I can tell with my foreheadpathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.50,0:13:32.53,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.41,0:13:35.85,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I can't! I can't say it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.29,0:13:39.47,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,If... If it goes like all the other times...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.05,0:13:44.17,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I won't laugh at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.20,0:13:49.64,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Yes, yes, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.85,0:13:52.51,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I just felt something on my alien radar!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.51,0:13:54.14,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I know where a card is!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.47,0:13:56.64,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,It must be up on the roof!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.50,0:14:00.15,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it's so nice up here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.15,0:14:01.99,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,The sky is so blue!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.99,0:14:03.56,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it, Umika?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.56,0:14:05.67,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Akeuchi-san, with the sky as her backdrop,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.67,0:14:09.91,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,seems so unbound, gentle, \Nstrong, and unfamiliar.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.64,0:14:13.45,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,And I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.04,0:14:17.91,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,A-Ake...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.16,0:14:21.20,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Akeuchi-san, h-h-he...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.67,0:14:24.42,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.42,0:14:28.49,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,My name is U-Umika Konohoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.77,0:14:32.94,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm an Earthling, born on Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.94,0:14:35.91,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,M-M-My height is 151 centimeters,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.91,0:14:37.20,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,a-and my weight...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.20,0:14:39.44,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, th-th-that part's a secret!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.75,0:14:43.67,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,My... My hobby is reading novels.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.67,0:14:47.44,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I like sci-fi and m-mystery stories!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.44,0:14:51.57,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,A-A-Also, I'm a little good at swimming.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.57,0:14:53.45,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,A-And... And...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.83,0:14:57.26,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,m-my lifelong dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.26,0:15:00.72,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,is to build a rocket to go to o-outer space,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.72,0:15:04.71,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,and find aliens who will be my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.31,0:15:10.23,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I h-hope we can get along!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.17,0:15:16.91,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Umika, thanks for telling me \Nso much about yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.51,0:15:20.87,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I think your dream is really awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.00,0:15:23.91,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,My words...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.91,0:15:26.35,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,They really reached her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.69,0:15:30.61,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,You've got a dream, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.61,0:15:32.86,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,How nice! How awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.20,0:15:35.60,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Well, since I'm an alien,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.60,0:15:39.44,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I need to go back to my home planet someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.44,0:15:41.45,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,You want to go to outer space,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.45,0:15:44.05,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,and I need to get back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.05,0:15:45.13,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.48,0:15:48.86,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,if we both chase after the same dream, \Nit's a bargain! Two for the price of one!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.86,0:15:49.76,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,A bargain?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.76,0:15:50.88,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.88,0:15:53.50,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like if we stick together, \Nit'll be a bargain!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.50,0:15:55.72,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Let's work hard and set our sights on space!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.01,0:15:56.92,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,'Kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.92,0:15:58.22,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.22,0:16:01.08,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.70,0:16:02.73,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.48,0:16:06.23,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Hop! Hop! Hop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.23,0:16:07.32,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.63,0:16:12.20,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Told ya! I knew it was on the roof!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.20,0:16:15.32,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Her alien radar sure is reliable!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.76,0:16:19.40,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, what task does our card hold?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.03,0:16:18.54,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,397)\fs30\fnComic Sans MS\bord3\c&H262926&\3c&HFEFBFB&}Scavenger hunt game
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.54,0:16:20.04,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(271,1)\fs30\fnComic Sans MS\bord3\c&H262926&\3c&HFEFBFB&}Talk about your dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.48,0:16:32.17,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Akeuchi-san is incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.62,0:16:34.84,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Superhuman physical ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.84,0:16:35.93,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,As well as...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.11,0:16:39.18,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,superhuman mental ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.11,0:16:40.18,DefaultTop,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't eat during class and fall asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.18,0:16:43.69,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,There's no doubt that \NAkeuchi-san is an alien!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.84,0:16:47.19,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,It's so nice out today!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.19,0:16:49.84,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Yu Akeuchi-san is an alien.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.84,0:16:52.69,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,And she can also use telepathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.90,0:16:57.09,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,When you think of aliens, the first thing \Nthat comes to mind is the classic Grey...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.32,0:16:56.20,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30\fnArial Black\c&H3C2CBF&\3c&H24205C&\bord1.5\pos(252.667,228)\frz12.55}Grey
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.09,0:16:58.70,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,but she doesn't look like that at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.36,0:17:02.78,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Is she trying to mimic \Nthe form of an Earthling?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.78,0:17:05.62,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she has some \Nundercover mission here on Earth?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.62,0:17:07.29,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Akeuchi-san's secret...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.29,0:17:09.46,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna ask her! I wanna ask her!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.46,0:17:10.71,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, go right ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.71,0:17:12.70,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.70,0:17:14.84,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,You looked like you wanted\N to ask me something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.78,0:17:18.40,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.75,0:17:21.73,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,A-Aren't you thirsty?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.73,0:17:22.85,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Here, a drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.85,0:17:25.10,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a big, fat wuss!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.40,0:17:29.58,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Umika!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.28,0:17:31.36,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.84,0:17:33.36,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Did she leave already?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.59,0:17:35.61,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Umika!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.61,0:17:39.60,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm definitely not tailing \Nor stalking her, here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.60,0:17:41.40,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,But... But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.66,0:17:51.50,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1026,304)\fs32\fnArial Black\bord2\c&HF2927B&\3c&H3F271C&\pos(76,134)}Wuss
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.18,0:17:46.21,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worried that if I insensitively pry into \Nher secret, she'll end up avoiding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.21,0:17:49.53,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,But that's still no excuse to follow her...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.44,0:17:52.00,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Well, whatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.00,0:17:54.17,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I'll look for her on my way home!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.17,0:17:56.47,DefaultTop,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Umika!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.17,0:17:58.33,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh yeah, Akeuchi-san has her alien radar.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.33,0:18:00.64,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm not careful, she might find me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.41,0:18:04.91,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I'll conceal my presence \Nso she doesn't notice me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.91,0:18:07.35,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Hold my breath and empty my mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.41,0:18:11.64,Narration,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,And thus, I lost sight of Akeuchi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.41,0:18:18.00,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,There you are, Umika!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.53,0:18:20.98,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I looked all over for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.98,0:18:22.28,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Let's walk home together!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.70,0:18:25.08,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... I'm so sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.08,0:18:29.33,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for... f-finding...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.33,0:18:31.04,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry I was late!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.63,0:18:32.92,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.92,0:18:35.77,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Do you want to come over to my house?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.42,0:18:38.45,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's more like my base than my house!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.45,0:18:39.93,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Feel free to come visit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.93,0:18:41.58,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,A-A-Are you sure?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.58,0:18:44.93,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Letting me enter y-your base so easily...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.18,0:18:51.97,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.97,0:18:53.34,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Cool, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.31,0:18:56.19,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,It's a lighthouse, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.60,0:18:59.66,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,A-Akeuchi-san, is this where...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.66,0:19:01.70,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Yep! I live here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.70,0:19:04.89,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,It's a perfect spot for catching fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.89,0:19:07.02,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me she's living off the land?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.02,0:19:10.16,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,If I had the equipment, \NI could keep one as a pet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.16,0:19:11.96,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,She just wants to watch them...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.06,0:19:16.05,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Here! Come right in!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.05,0:19:17.84,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,E-Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.12,0:19:20.79,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave your bag around there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.84,0:19:23.34,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fnTimes New Roman\bord2\c&H1B1510&\3c&H6A5E5E&}PUBLIC ENTRY PROHIBITED\NBEYOND THIS POINT\N{\fs16}Coast Guard Headquarters
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.34,0:19:25.94,DefaultTop,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Um, where's the light?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.78,0:19:26.72,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Is she using an abandoned \Nlighthouse as her base?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.69,0:19:29.41,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, wrong one!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.23,0:19:33.61,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still getting used to the place!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.98,0:19:35.77,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,An alien language notepad?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.77,0:19:37.98,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I can read \Nwhat it says on the cover!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.30,0:19:41.33,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Space...  voyage log?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.86,0:19:44.37,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! That's private!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.37,0:19:46.38,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.38,0:19:47.74,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just messing with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.80,0:19:49.75,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,You see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.80,0:19:54.75,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Truth is, I don't have any memories \Nof my time before Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.75,0:19:59.37,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,When I came to, I found \Nmyself in this lighthouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.78,0:20:04.75,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Look, the last page of my voyage log.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.75,0:20:09.52,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,It ends after changing course to Earth and \Ndescribing the spaceship breaking down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.35,0:20:13.60,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,And when I woke up, I looked like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.77,0:20:16.73,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(777,514)\fnTimes New Roman\fs22\an8\c&H6F5031&\3c&HBB8F47&\bord1.5\b0\frz8.348\pos(391.11,66.89)}Student ID
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.77,0:20:16.73,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(777,514)\fnTimes New Roman\fs10\an8\c&H6F5031&\3c&HA87E40&\bord1.5\b0\frz8.348\pos(389.41,116.21)}Name:       {\fs15}Yu Akeuchi
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.77,0:20:16.73,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(777,514)\fnTimes New Roman\fs10\an8\c&H573D1C&\3c&H98713A&\bord1.5\b0\frz8.348\pos(396.16,151.76)}Program: General Education
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.77,0:20:16.73,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(777,514)\fnTimes New Roman\fs8\an7\c&H573D1C&\3c&H8D6934&\bord1.5\b0\frz8.348\pos(346.02,177.98)}This is to certify that the above-mentioned individual\N\Nis an enrolled student at this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.77,0:20:16.73,Signs,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(777,514)\fnTimes New Roman\fs12\an8\c&H241608&\3c&H735322&\bord1.5\b0\frz8.348\pos(415.06,235.74)}Fujinomisaki High School
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.60,0:20:16.23,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,and I was holding a high \Nschool student handbook.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.01,0:20:23.12,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,So there must be something \NI came here to accomplish,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.12,0:20:25.53,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,but I can't remember any of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.33,0:20:28.85,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm such a useless alien!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.85,0:20:29.59,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Umika!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.59,0:20:31.29,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be disappointed in me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.29,0:20:34.28,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'd never be disappointed...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.28,0:20:38.04,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Is she telling me this because \NI wanted to learn her secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.80,0:20:42.34,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I bet she must have gone through so much,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.34,0:20:45.05,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,but it had never occurred to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.51,0:21:01.96,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for not realizing \Nhow much trouble you've faced.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.82,0:21:06.07,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I know living on Earth can't be easy for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.43,0:21:10.58,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,but I'll do everything I can to help you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.04,0:21:15.91,DefaultItalics,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I'll even make a rocket \Nso that you can go back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.53,0:21:17.69,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Umika...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.03,0:21:24.09,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry I couldn't \Ntell you to your face...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.84,0:21:28.27,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Umika! I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.27,0:21:29.83,Default,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Besties for life!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.83,0:21:32.07,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,A-Akeuchi-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.07,0:21:35.14,Narration,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,And that's how I, Umika Konohoshi,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.14,0:21:38.49,Narration,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,came to share the same dream \Nas Akeuchi-san, an alien,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.49,0:21:41.86,Narration,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,as we set our sights for outer space!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.17,0:21:48.90,Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Is there... someone here?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.12,0:23:22.42,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Akeuchi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.42,0:23:24.92,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,A-Akeuchi-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.80,0:23:27.42,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,A-A-Ake...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.42,0:23:31.57,DefaultItalics,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, the forehead really is the strongest.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.10,0:23:34.93,Default,Umika,0000,0000,0000,,Akeuchi-san!
